{"tid":627402,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"C朗落井下石：保方算吧啦","createTime":"2018-04-13T02:58:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-13T08:16:18.000Z","uid":54373,"like":2,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"112aa239c7c5ef0cf44c33099dbfb574f72c1cf0","tid":627402,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T02:58:13.000Z","msg":"2018-04-13體育<br />\n<br />\n　　(星島日報報道)因一個爭議性十二碼，祖雲達斯門將保方再一次無緣歐聯錦標。操刀的皇家馬德里射手C朗拿度不但沒同理心，還批評保方等投訴無理。同時，他今仗射入關鍵十二碼後，成為歐聯史上首位連續十一仗士哥的球員。<br />\n<br />\n　　外界普遍對保方的遭遇深感同情，C朗卻落井下石：「我不明白他們為甚麼要投訴？若沒有犯規，盧卡斯華斯基斯已經將球射入網。今仗貝拿迪亞等祖雲達斯球員多次從後侵犯我們。」或許自知禍從口出，他賽後在球員通道跟保方擁抱，以表同情。"},{"pid":"9811f7d7b776839658c31ebc4a20f90ec6dbd520","tid":627402,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T06:40:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d85cec2a1520865902499d565158426a4a775bc7","tid":627402,"uid":46507,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T06:42:01.000Z","msg":"邊句有錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"770f788ceaa32f46ec507293841f802c3b3aa4ff","tid":627402,"uid":63936,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T06:43:39.000Z","msg":"句句事實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"773b72392fad11d32709fdbfd22726f8398cb4c6","tid":627402,"uid":16343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d85cec2a1520865902499d565158426a4a775bc7","tid":627402,"uid":46507,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T06:42:01.000Z","msg":"邊句有錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T06:43:43.000Z","msg":"華斯基斯射就難D講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31321ccfc5d1ac0454c1f3e8b9deb37a4984ee57","tid":627402,"uid":172709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T08:07:57.000Z","msg":"駁唔到添。。"},{"pid":"5c73f3f5d3